{
  "stem": "9262.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in our spare time, we were trained-- trained in gardening, in agriculture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had lectures given by tutors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the meantime, my family was in the ghetto itself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children's colony was also in the ghetto, but on the edge, on the edge of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one day, my mother came running with my little brother, because the bigger brother was working.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she told me that my father has passed away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, he had typhoid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also, he died of hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we had very meager rations in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people tended to eat everything in one go because they were afraid that the goods, the food, would be stolen from them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they said, well, if we are dying, we might as well have a good meal, and we die in any case.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the death certificate-- the Germans did not allow to put typhoid or starvation on the de-- on the death certificate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody died from natural causes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was the norm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even now, so many years after the war, when the Poles issue the death certificate, no mention was made cause of death-- absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my little brother was staying at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I and my older brother-- we went after the hearse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now when we came to the cemetery and they were digging in a grave, there was my aunt, my uncle, and one of my cousins, and just us two boys.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were many people on the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jewish law requires that if somebody says kaddish, provided there are 10 people-- 10 male within the vicinity of hearing the name of [? amen, ?] you may recite kaddish.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, kaddish is forbidden to be said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my uncle said, your father is dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
